title: GIDDY-UP, GO!!.... to this stunning studio in St Paul
posting_body: ['Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule a tour today!', '"Giddy-up, Go before its gone!"', ' Celebrate Summer in this studio overlooking Mears Park!!', ' Follow the Magical GNOMES to LowerTown...here is their perfect perch for you and your "city kitty!"', ' to watch the seasons in the park--this East-facing 7th floor studio apartment features a view overlooking our beautiful Mears Park, with shimmering lights in the trees!', ' The apartment also features large closet spaces, and plenty of natural sunlight!', 'Get a work out in using our 24/7 private Fitness Center and Studio, relax in our indoor heated pool and get toasty warm in our sauna.', 'Mears Park Place is owned and managed by Bigos Management.', 'Conveniently located in trendy Lowertown across from Mears Park, you can walk the skyway down to the river and bike along the Bike trails through the city parks.', 'We are just 2 blocks from Union Depot and the light rail station, which can take you through St. Paul and connects to Minneapolis and the University campus, as well as the airport.', 'Mears Park Place Apartments features:', '* Indoor Pool', '* Sun Patio', '*', 'Rec Room', '* Sauna', '* Tanning Bed', '* Party Room', '* 24hr gym with fitness studio', '* Underground Parking', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'to schedule your guided tour today!', 'Please reference apartment #624', '*Pricing and availability are both determined by requested move-in date, cannot be guaranteed due to on-site leasing activity, and are subject to change at any time.']
